      <b data-is-speakable>Fighting COVID-19 Is Like 'Whack-A-Mole,' Writer Ed Yong Says : Shots - Health News</b>   <b data-is-speakable><em>Atlantic </em>writer Ed Yong warned of a global pandemic two years ago<em>.</em> He says scientists are still working to understand how COVID-19 travels through air — and whether more of us should be wearing masks.</b>
